We have a few concerts lined up over the next few months. There is nothing live seeing a band or musician you like perform live. We're going to see [Iron and Wine](https://ironandwine.com) in a couple of weeks at the [Uptown Theater](http://uptowntheater.com).  {{< apple-music url="https://music.apple.com/us/album/light-verse/1726083469" >}} Then, two days later, We're going to see[ My Morning Jacket ](https://www.mymorningjacket.com)at the same venue. I love the Uptown, it's a relatively small, brightly painted old theater, we've seen hundred of shows there over the years. My Morning Jacket's latest album, Is, is fantastic {{< apple-music url="https://music.apple.com/us/album/is/1786273438" >}}

I'm also going to the [Record Bar](https://www.therecordbar.com) in May to see another favorite [Messer Chups](https://messerchupsofficial.bandcamp.com). {{< apple-music url="https://music.apple.com/us/album/dark-side-of-paradise/1739156722">}}
Messer Chups is a Russian Surf Punk band who do a lot of fun covers along with originals. They are a blast to see live! 

